Maintainer: Nima Hejazi <nh@nimahejazi.org>
Description: Estimators of causal effects of stochastic interventions arising
    in the presence of mediation, including estimating equation, substitution,
    and re-weighting estimators of the natural direct effect under incremental
    propensity score interventions and modified treatment policies (Díaz and
    Hejazi; 2018+ (submitted). <doi:>).
